Hello and happy Friday, everyone! :wave:  I’m Cheska, currently Chief Growth Officer at <https://butter.us|Butter>. We’re building an all-in-one tool for workshops to help facilitators run high-energy, collaborative sessions with ease.

My background is in digital marketing and strategic comms planning. I’ve heard a lot of good things about this community and I’m super excited to be part of it. Can’t wait to meet and learn from all of you! :blush::tada:

text: Hi Everyone :call_me_hand: I’m Jeremy - I run a marketing and communications agency based in Washington DC. We specialize in working with B2B service-based businesses (private equity, cyber, technology, consulting, healthcare, etc.) and becoming their marketing/comms infrastructure from exec level engagement through research, production, execution. Separately, I run 2 podcasts/shows that are a lot of fun. :headphones: :calling: I’m here to learn and get more involved in these digital communities (meet some new people), as well as add value wherever I am able.  Cheers!

:upside_down_face: Hello, community! I’m Victor, I run a small but growing marketing agency on Vancouver Island.
Besides serving clients with SEO, content strategy and WordPress optimizations.
:woman_in_lotus_position: I’m also creating an on+offline yoga community centered on learning the philosophy of yoga, but bringing it to the modern world.
:nerd_face: The final hat I wear is of a spreadsheet whiz. I’m about to launch a site of useful templates and Excel apps for small businesses.
My friend has raved about this group so I’m excited to be a part of it, contribute and meeting some of y’all!

elements.text:
Hello, community! I’m Victor, I run a small but growing marketing agency on Vancouver Island.
Besides serving clients with SEO, content strategy and WordPress optimizations.
I’m also creating an on+offline yoga community centered on learning the philosophy of yoga, but bringing it to the modern world.

The final hat I wear is of a spreadsheet whiz. I’m about to launch a site of useful templates and Excel apps for small businesses.
My friend has raved about this group so I’m excited to be a part of it, contribute and meeting some of y’all!
